response.overview: Black Butt Jungle is a video about the life of Domonique Simone, her loves and career in front of the camera. You get a real insight into what makes this sexual animal tick, as well as some tasty sex scenes opposite Veronica Brazil, Peter North and Joe Verducci among others. BLACK BUTT JUNGLE takes you deep inside her darkest desires. See the animal hunger. Feel the ultimate passion and learn her most intimate secrets of this queen of the jungle.
response.title: Black Butt Jungle
